---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContentSection from '@/components/ui/ContentSection.astro';
import { navConfig } from '@/config/navigation';
---

<Layout
  title="Artricenter | Clínica de Reumatología en Ciudad de México — Especialistas en Artrosis, Artritis y Fibromialgia"
  description="Clínica reumatológica en CDMX con más de 15 años de experiencia. Diagnóstico y tratamiento integral de artrosis, artritis reumatoide, fibromialgia y enfermedades reumáticas. Agenda tu valoración hoy."
  currentPage="/"
  jsonLd={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "MedicalClinic",
    "name": "Artricenter",
    "url": "https://artricenter.com.mx",
    "description": "Clínica reumatológica en Ciudad de México con especialistas en artrosis, artritis reumatoide y fibromialgia.",
    "founder": {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "Dr. Alexander Fernández Portello",
      "jobTitle": "Director Médico",
      "knowsAbout": "Rheumatology"
    },
    "employee": [
      {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Dra. Cira Cibelis Calzadilla Columbie",
        "jobTitle": "Director Médico de Artricenter Atizapán",
        "knowsAbout": "Rheumatology"
      },
      {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Dr. Justo Méndez",
        "jobTitle": "Director Médico de Artricenter Viaducto",
        "knowsAbout": "Rheumatology"
      }
    ]
  }}
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Carousel de banners -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16 rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden relative" id="hero-carousel">
      <div class="carousel-track" id="carousel-track">
        <div class="carousel-slide is-active">
          <img src="/assets/images/hero/banner-1.webp" alt="Artricenter - Especialistas en enfermedades reumáticas" width="807" height="234" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" />
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/hero/banner-2.webp" alt="Artricenter - Tratamiento integral" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/hero/joints-banner.avif" alt="Artricenter - Cuidado de articulaciones" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-btn carousel-prev" aria-label="Anterior">&#10094;</button>
      <button class="carousel-btn carousel-next" aria-label="Siguiente">&#10095;</button>
      <div class="carousel-dots" id="carousel-dots">
        <span class="carousel-dot active" data-index="0"></span>
        <span class="carousel-dot" data-index="1"></span>
        <span class="carousel-dot" data-index="2"></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sección introductoria con texto -->
    <section id="artricenter" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h1 class="sr-only">Artricenter — Clínica de Reumatología en Ciudad de México</h1>
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-8">Artricenter</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6">
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgb(0, 83, 161))"></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="background-color: rgb(0, 83, 161)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(83, 175, 49)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(242, 144, 88)"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgb(242, 144, 88))"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-justify text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed px-4">
        <p>
          En Artricenter somos especialistas en el diagnóstico y tratamiento integral de enfermedades reumáticas.
        </p>

        <p>
          Entendemos que el dolor, la inflamación y la rigidez no solo afectan tus articulaciones, sino también tu rutina diaria, tu independencia y tu bienestar emocional.
        </p>

        <p>
          Nuestro enfoque médico está basado en una valoración clínica detallada, diagnóstico preciso y planes de tratamiento personalizados, diseñados para aliviar el dolor, mejorar la función articular y prevenir el avance de la enfermedad.
        </p>

        <p>
          Trabajamos con un modelo de atención médica centrada en el paciente, donde cada caso se estudia de manera individual para ofrecer soluciones seguras, efectivas y respaldadas por evidencia médica.
        </p>

        <p>
          Atendemos padecimientos como osteoartrosis, artritis reumatoide, fibromialgia y otras condiciones que afectan tu movilidad y calidad de vida.
        </p>

        <p>
          Nuestro compromiso es acompañarte en cada etapa de tu recuperación para que vuelvas a moverte con confianza y seguridad.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Botón CTA -->
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a
          href="/tratamiento-medico-integral"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold text-lg rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 active:translate-y-0 active:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform"
          style="background-color: rgb(0, 83, 161)"
          onmouseenter="this.style.backgroundColor='rgb(0, 70, 135)'"
          onmouseleave="this.style.backgroundColor='rgb(0, 83, 161)'"
        >
          Tratamiento Médico Integral
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Separador final estilizado -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-16 mb-12">
        <div class="h-1 w-40 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-1 w-40 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent via-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sección Nuestra Historia — Línea del Tiempo Interactiva -->
    <section id="nuestra-historia" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <div class="timeline-section-header">
          <div class="timeline-header-line">
            <span class="timeline-header-arrow">▶</span>
            <span class="timeline-header-dots"></span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-600">Línea de tiempo de Artricenter</h2>
          <div class="timeline-header-line">
            <span class="timeline-header-dots"></span>
            <span class="timeline-header-arrow">◀</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Texto introductorio de historia -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-justify text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed px-4 mb-12">
        <p>
          Iniciamos actividades en el año 2006.
        </p>

        <p>
          Debido a nuestro éxito, creamos el 2 de septiembre del 2014, una nueva sucursal en Atizapán, Estado de México.
        </p>

        <p>
          En 2020 aperturamos nuestra sucursal en Viaducto, extendiendo así la cobertura de Atención Integral para Pacientes con Enfermedades Reumáticas (PAIPER).
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline Container -->
      <div class="timeline-container relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <!-- Línea central vertical (fondo) -->
        <div class="timeline-line-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <!-- Línea central vertical (progreso) -->
        <div class="timeline-line-progress" id="timeline-progress" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <!-- Hito 1: 2006 - La Raza -->
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-left timeline-item--1" data-side="left">
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <span class="timeline-year">2006</span>
              <h3 class="timeline-title">La Raza</h3>
              <p class="timeline-text">
                Iniciamos actividades.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-circle">
            <img src="/assets/images/branches/la-raza.webp" alt="Artricenter La Raza — Inicio de actividades en 2006" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-empty"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Conector 1 → 2 -->
        <div class="timeline-connector timeline-connector--right" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="100 5 600 50" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path class="timeline-connector-path" d="M230,5 Q300,45 470,105" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="6,4" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>
            <polygon class="timeline-arrowhead" points="470,100 455,94 455,106" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Hito 2: 2015 - Atizapán -->
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-right timeline-item--2" data-side="right">
          <div class="timeline-empty"></div>
          <div class="timeline-circle">
            <img src="/assets/images/branches/atizapan.webp" alt="Artricenter Atizapán — Inaugurada en 2015" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <span class="timeline-year">2015</span>
              <h3 class="timeline-title">Atizapán</h3>
              <p class="timeline-text">
                Gracias al éxito obtenido en nuestra sucursal la raza creamos una nueva sucursal en Atizapán, Estado de México.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Conector 2 → 3 -->
        <div class="timeline-connector timeline-connector--left" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="100 5 600 50" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path class="timeline-connector-path" d="M470,5 Q340,45 230,105" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="6,4" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>
            <polygon class="timeline-arrowhead" points="230,100 245,94 245,106" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Hito 3: 2020 - Viaducto -->
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-left timeline-item--3" data-side="left">
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <span class="timeline-year">2020</span>
              <h3 class="timeline-title">Viaducto</h3>
              <p class="timeline-text">
                Aperturamos nuestra sucursal en Viaducto, extendiendo así la cobertura de Atención Integral para Pacientes con Enfermedades Reumáticas (PAIPER).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-circle">
            <img src="/assets/images/branches/viaducto.webp" alt="Artricenter Viaducto — Apertura en 2020" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-empty"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Conector 3 → 4 -->
        <div class="timeline-connector timeline-connector--right" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="100 5 600 50" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path class="timeline-connector-path" d="M230,5 Q300,45 470,105" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="6,4" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"/>
            <polygon class="timeline-arrowhead" points="470,100 455,94 455,106" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Hito 4: Actualidad -->
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-right timeline-item--4" data-side="right">
          <div class="timeline-empty"></div>
          <div class="timeline-circle timeline-circle--current">
            <svg class="w-1/2 h-1/2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-card timeline-card--current">
              <span class="timeline-year">Actualidad</span>
              <h3 class="timeline-title">Actualidad</h3>
              <!-- Tabla de porcentajes -->
              <div class="timeline-stats">
                <div class="timeline-stat-row">
                  <span class="timeline-stat-label">Osteoartrosis</span>
                  <div class="timeline-stat-bar-bg">
                    <div class="timeline-stat-bar" data-percent="91"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="timeline-stat-value">91%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-stat-row">
                  <span class="timeline-stat-label">Artritis Reumatoide</span>
                  <div class="timeline-stat-bar-bg">
                    <div class="timeline-stat-bar" data-percent="67"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="timeline-stat-value">67%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-stat-row">
                  <span class="timeline-stat-label">Fibromialgia</span>
                  <div class="timeline-stat-bar-bg">
                    <div class="timeline-stat-bar" data-percent="65"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="timeline-stat-value">65%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-stat-row">
                  <span class="timeline-stat-label">Espondiloartritis</span>
                  <div class="timeline-stat-bar-bg">
                    <div class="timeline-stat-bar" data-percent="76"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="timeline-stat-value">76%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-stat-row">
                  <span class="timeline-stat-label">Reumatismo de Partes Blandas</span>
                  <div class="timeline-stat-bar-bg">
                    <div class="timeline-stat-bar" data-percent="89"></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="timeline-stat-value">89%</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Separador inferior -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-12">
        <div class="h-1 w-40 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-1 w-40 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent via-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sección Enfermedades que Tratamos -->
    <section id="enfermedades" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-8">Mejora de Dolor por Enfermedad Tratada</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6">
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgb(0, 83, 161))"></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="background-color: rgb(0, 83, 161)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(83, 175, 49)"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: rgb(242, 144, 88)"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-1 w-40 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgb(242, 144, 88))"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 px-4">
        El COLEGIO AMERICANO DE REUMATOLOGIA (ACR) considera un resultado positivo si se logra una mejora del 20 % en el recuento de articulaciones dolorosas o inflamadas.
      </p>

      <!-- Grid de enfermedades -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">

        <!-- 1. Osteoartrosis — 91% -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 border-l-4" style="border-left-color: rgb(0, 83, 161)">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.15), rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.05))">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: rgb(0, 83, 161)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Osteoartrosis</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3 leading-relaxed">Desgaste progresivo del cartílago articular que causa dolor, rigidez y limitación del movimiento.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Eficacia del tratamiento</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: rgb(0, 83, 161)">91%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full h-2.5 bg-gray-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-1000" style="width: 91%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(0, 83, 161), rgb(0, 120, 200))"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Reumatismo de Partes Blandas — 89% -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 border-l-4" style="border-left-color: rgb(83, 175, 49)">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(83, 175, 49, 0.15), rgba(83, 175, 49, 0.05))">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: rgb(83, 175, 49)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Reumatismo de Partes Blandas</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3 leading-relaxed">Afecciones que involucran tendones, ligamentos, bolsas sinoviales y músculos causando dolor e inflamación localizada.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Eficacia del tratamiento</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: rgb(83, 175, 49)">89%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full h-2.5 bg-gray-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-1000" style="width: 89%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(83, 175, 49), rgb(120, 200, 80))"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. Espondiloartritis — 76% -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 border-l-4" style="border-left-color: rgb(0, 83, 161)">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.15), rgba(0, 83, 161, 0.05))">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: rgb(0, 83, 161)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Espondiloartritis</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3 leading-relaxed">Grupo de enfermedades inflamatorias que afectan principalmente la columna vertebral y las articulaciones sacroilíacas.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Eficacia del tratamiento</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: rgb(0, 83, 161)">76%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full h-2.5 bg-gray-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-1000" style="width: 76%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(0, 83, 161), rgb(0, 120, 200))"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Artritis Reumatoide — 67% -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 border-l-4" style="border-left-color: rgb(83, 175, 49)">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(83, 175, 49, 0.15), rgba(83, 175, 49, 0.05))">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: rgb(83, 175, 49)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 11.5V14m0-2.5v-6a1.5 1.5 0 113 0m-3 6a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0v2a7.5 7.5 0 0015 0v-5a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-6-3V11m0-5.5v-1a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v1m0 0V11m0-5.5a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v3m0 0V11"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Artritis Reumatoide</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3 leading-relaxed">Enfermedad autoinmune que causa inflamación crónica de las articulaciones, dolor y deformidad progresiva.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Eficacia del tratamiento</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: rgb(83, 175, 49)">67%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full h-2.5 bg-gray-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-1000" style="width: 67%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(83, 175, 49), rgb(120, 200, 80))"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 5. Fibromialgia — 65% -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 border-l-4" style="border-left-color: rgb(242, 144, 88)">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(242, 144, 88, 0.15), rgba(242, 144, 88, 0.05))">
